data.description: Wow! A Remarkable Renovation of a Beautiful Home. This 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home has it all. Upon entering the foyer, you will immediately appreciate this homes features. The delightful living room leads to the Dining room off the newly remodeled kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances and granite countertops. Love your mornings in the spacious Breakfast area with Large Windows looking into backyard & Large Family room with a Fireplace. Large enclosed Sunroom looks out to the backyard. You'll also find an Amazing Bonus room & workshop. Spacious Bedrooms upstairs with Beautiful Hardwoods Floors. Fresh Paint, New Carpet, and roof under 2 years old. Great school districts, close to highways, easy access to the airport and all that Atlanta has to offer. Completely move-in ready!
